Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能和六花一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.91,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一決勝負吧  冒牌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  想打架的話我不會客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:21.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被忽略了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:03:00.80,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,500)\pos(95,386)}第七集{\fs32}{\alpha&HFF}\Naaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}Paradise Lost\N{\fs0}追憶的… 樂園喪失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就暈車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你就是小學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  看看外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往遠處的綠色看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候最需要的就是閱讀黑暗聖典的名句
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將魔物祛除…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈之…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是反作用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間就在那邊  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是男生陪著去的話會被人誤會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要…  冒牌貨的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就到了  給我忍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瀕死之時為敵人所救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色  你也來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都知道你在看哪裡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是給點反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  難道你也暈車了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我接受過訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼不說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在轉轉轉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰錘颶風…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你閉嘴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼連我也要遭殃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很會照顧人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想照顧人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你也跟著吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小鳥遊同學邀請我們來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要回老家  問我們想不想一起來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是非要跟過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這裡有什麼特別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這種事不是很常見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入高中後  跟中學時的男朋友兩地分離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成遠距離戀愛什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那就是修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修羅場是一種強力的結界魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛…  嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向邪王真眼  起誓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會不會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十花小姐  是六花的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的房子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說小鳥遊同學家很有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎大家遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們平時一直都受小鳥遊同學照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次還被邀請到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒給你們添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花還在玩海盜遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟現在很流行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  還以為能變得正經一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶  請給大家深褐液體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:07:00.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}aaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}Dark Brown Liquid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點心意不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要客氣  隨意就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  你就像個大媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的魔獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好大的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  從哪兒來的狗狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  快把她撕碎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡倒是沒那麼多擺設嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來與無形境界線的另一端通信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪兒找來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真虧你能找到這種東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想過搬到現在的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被聖料理人拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想啊  按照你的說法就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎正在此地探測某種氣息  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡本來就不是我的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是管理局的總部  敵人的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前  我被帶到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看是一座普普通通的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡卻有著能抹消無形境界線存在的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神攻擊加上負荷增大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽不太懂  但看來是發生過什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打破這個結界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要邪王真眼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年你會去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李我就放這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你的朋友們說要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓朋友太擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小森大人  竟然穿兩件式的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你穿的這又算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連泳衣都是純白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我只有這件嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…  眼睛裡進海水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海怪克拉肯就潛伏在這片海中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kraken{\alpha&HFF}aaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是測試這套海戰用魔導裝威力的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備上那套魔導裝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海中也能擁有平時3.88倍的活動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.88倍的活動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去游泳吧  枯茗學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你也沒怎麼說上話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  刻耳柏洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}aaaaa{\alpha}Cerberus
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：希臘神話中看守冥界入口的惡犬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會聽那傢伙的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啦  幹嘛要跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
