Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湛藍雙輪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.05,0:11:35.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rhonrad Zwei Hellblau
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們將要前往無形境界線的聚點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐上來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就穿成這樣去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃離聖料理人的監視
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣程度的偽裝是必須…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是變成這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去她的父親那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身都好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被聖光打敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你不塗防曬霜還像那樣瘋玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  刻印已經完美形成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這是拿給我們吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
