Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:52.89,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正大黑_GBK\bord0\shad0\an7\fs72\frz19.358\pos(921,448)\c&H99BADE&}冒牌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時六花還太小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸讓我們先瞞著她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對六花來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸走得過於突然  沒有任何預兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她至今都不願意接受爸爸去世了的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固執地拒絕到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們的母親呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我和六花丟在婆家就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺為人很嚴肅  沒法接受六花那樣的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我也因為工作離開了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果過了兩年  她還是那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要找到無形境界線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打破這個結界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要邪王真眼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是十花小姐做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是幹這個的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來小鳥游同學的便當總是很豪華啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在班裡很有名的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  沒想到您竟然是在那家高級餐廳工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕六花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊開動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這道菜是加了乳酪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凸連乳酪也吃不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會吃那種帶著臭抹布味的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乳酪可是奶腐壞之後變成的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凸真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是連主人也畏懼的聖料理人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼神的威力非同小可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼最強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你受到了聖料理人的精神攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的勇太已經不是勇太了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是這麼認為的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  好歹我也是原黑炎掌控者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不想去找無形境界線了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要說謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  姐姐  還有爺爺奶奶都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就選我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她…  聖料理人一定會有所戒備的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃離這裡並非易事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候出發？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現…  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動到那棵樹上  然後下到樹的右邊躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒穿鞋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有穿  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉盆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是十花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你竟然會幫她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢  我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才那句話有點帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  你別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是危險人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:17:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  六花 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你去湛藍雙輪的藏匿之處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有大概十公里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…  有那麼遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為黑炎掌控者是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  果然是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別再提這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加速了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真正最強的是邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦  知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果六花和富樫君到現在也沒回來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十花小姐也不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛路上免不了坎坷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼坎坷？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  小凸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我想只是時間問題了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯茗學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前  你看見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸消失的那個夜晚  我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在境界線的另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他一定還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從境界線的另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直望著這裡  望著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於六花的話  我無法肯定  也無法反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是我的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸  還有大家一起住過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待售土地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發吧  現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迸裂吧  神經
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧  整個世界
